~FT+-----------------------------------------------------------------------------+
~FT   Command~RS  : copyto                                    ~FTPODnuts
~FT+-----------------------------------------------------------------------------+

~FT   Usage~RS    : copyto <user user user>
              then smail <message>

   You can send smail to users by typing usernames seperated by one 
   space.  This function is a great timesaver when you want to mail 
   the same information to multiple users.  This command establishes 
   a temp mailing list that will be used for the smail you send after
   you set the names by using copyto.

~FT+-----------------------------------------------------------------------------+
~FT   See also~RS : rmail, dmail, from, smail
~FT+-----------------------------------------------------------------------------+
